{
  "stem": "1419.1",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The minute-- the minute the Germans came in 1939, they requested all the Jews move out from Zakopane, because it was like a-- like special made for Germans to, to come for the winter, for the winter and the summer resort.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And Jews were not allowed to live in Zakopane.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Was Judenfrei.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we were shipped to Zakopane.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we was-- we were-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] we were-- [PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] we were put in the barracks.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Was a stone quarry.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And we had to work 12 hours a day in the stone quarry, from morning till night, not, not 12 hours, something.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "In the wintertime, we [? didn't ?] work 12 hours.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And we used to [INAUDIBLE] the, the big-- dynamite the big mountains, chop it up with [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And there used to be machines which they chopped up to a small, little, little gravel.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And there were-- there were little stones, bigger stones, and you know, [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And, and we loaded things on the trucks and shipped it on the big railroad tracks to a different part of, I guess, of the country, to which they build roads.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And I was there since-- from 1941 till 1942.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, I do.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The head of the Jewish council, Jewish Judenrat, was Ginsberg.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I forget the name-- Ginsberg.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "First name, I don't remember.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Before the war he was-- he was-- in the Jewish community, he used to be a-- what they call it, a [? expediter. ?] In other words, he used to-- they used to have horses and bring merchandise from, from the railroad to the stores.",
      "word_count": 45
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "What would you call that?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It's, it's not like a moving company, like-- you know, what they call it?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "What they call-- would you call it?",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
